imdb.plot outline: A supernatural based action-adventure turned political thriller begins when we follow the life a U.S. Army civil affairs doctor who specializes in exotic diseases. She returns home to LA after she is unknowingly infected by a mysterious virus that she is told may have turned her into a werewolf. She must go on the run after the death of her husband with an ex cop wanted for murder and that is the least of her worries. Who or what is all behind this?
